<div id="title">Vision</div>

<p>

<em>Our goal:</em> to take <span class="cnx">Connexions</span> to a
<em>critical mass</em> on a <em>global scale</em>.

<!-- 
<em>Our goal:</em> to create the richest and most complex continuum of 
knowledge in existence.  Anywhere.
-->

</p>

<p>

We intend to achieve this through a multifaceted approach that 
optimizes the use of:

</p>

<ul>
<li>a massive commons of <em>high-quality content</em></li>
<li>numerous and <em>diverse subject areas</em></li>
<li><em>large, global and grassroots communities</em> of authors, 
instructors, and students <em>working collaboratively</em></li>
<li><em>grassroots organization</em></li>
<li>scalable software and organizational <em>infrastructures</em> to
foster collaboration among authors, instructors, and students</li>
</ul>

<p>

We will also launch a sustainable, non-profit
<em>&#147;dot-org&#148;</em> when <span class="cnx">Connexions</span>
has grown beyond the bounds of our current institutional home at Rice
University.

</p>

